{"tid":226964,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"認真, C朗算唔算近廿年最好既足球員?","createTime":"2017-05-02T21:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T08:46:54.000Z","uid":22580,"like":9,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48a6dbe19eaeedd5e0a87ddc4824cfb377f2e5eb","tid":226964,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T21:40:11.000Z","msg":"廿年前未睇波唔評論 <br />\n<br />\nC朗集所有於一身： <br />\n球味, 星味, 個人技術, 入球能力, 罰球, 體能, 速度, 頭鎚, <br />\n你可以話好多頂級球星都有上面既野, 但極少數有埋下面既野 <br />\n態度, 爭勝心, 樣貌, 身形, 高度, KEEP住最少六七年既巔峰狀態(呢樣係屈指可數) <br />\n<br />\n基本上既球會榮譽同個人榮譽都有： <br />\n英超, 世冠, 歐國, 歐冠, 西甲, 國王盃, 英足先生, 世足先生"},{"pid":"c3ee4d7b710e90b404f6561824e1aa445679dfe2","tid":226964,"uid":4028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T21:40:48.000Z","msg":"梅西勁啲"},{"pid":"35687e32f2d7e627faffb4696f3776277e127c47","tid":226964,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T21:41:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梅西勁啲</blockquote><br />\n冇歐國"},{"pid":"fcb30d3de21cbde9b294c1b7f3209ab172c70433","tid":226964,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T21:41:31.000Z","msg":"一句講晒 <br />\n美斯最勁"},{"pid":"ec5d030fd62d8fb588149235f6738a8c94cf59b0","tid":226964,"uid":49269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T21:41:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梅西勁啲</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9062f0f17586443319661eea6136276e627a3d2a","tid":226964,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T21:42:42.000Z","msg":"校長想燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d083e72b8c2ba4e930a74a61e96cf48a18f0a4","tid":226964,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T21:43:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>校長想燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學埋你啲衰野"},{"pid":"53504e24295512a4b4ea468dc717000bb1734a65","tid":226964,"uid":100689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re